## About
Hi. I'm goose121 and I sometimes code things. They're not often big things, they're never very polished things, but I make them. This is where I put my things. All of my projects are in the public domain, but if you use them, please do give credit.
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
